OL,3,CMinister wants landlords investigated
OL,4,Cover illegal tenancy deposits
OL,6,FStates' figures show that between 2020
OL,7,Fand 2023, nearly a fifth of deposits
OL,8,Fwere not submitted to the official
OL,9,FJersey scheme on time.
OL,11,FThe independent initiative is designed
OL,12,Fto give tenants greater security and
OL,13,Fmake it easier for them to recover
OL,14,Ftheir money at the end of their lease.
OL,16,FIt also allows deposits to be kept
OL,17,Fsafe while an independent assessment
OL,18,Fis carried out if there are any
OL,19,Fdisagreements over damages or rental
OL,20,Fpayments.
