OL,3,CMinister wants landlords investigated
OL,4,Cover illegal tenancy deposits
OL,6,FITV News has been told that Attorney
OL,7,FGeneral Mark Temple KC, who is
OL,8,Fresponsible for these types of cases,
OL,9,Fallegedly said prosecuting landlords
OL,10,Ffor this offence does not meet the
OL,11,Fpublic interest threshold.
OL,13,FITV News has contacted the States
OL,14,FGreffe about this and did not
OL,15,Fimmediately receive a response.
